flowchart TD
    Start([Start Binary Search]) --> CheckSorted{Is List Sorted?}
    CheckSorted -->|No| SortList[Sort List by ID<br/>Quick Sort O n log n]
    CheckSorted -->|Yes| InitVars[Initialize:<br/>left = 0<br/>right = size - 1<br/>comparisons = 0]
    SortList --> InitVars

    InitVars --> GetTarget[Get Target ID from User]
    GetTarget --> CheckBounds{left <= right}

    CheckBounds -->|Yes| IncrementComp[comparisons++]
    IncrementComp --> CalcMid[mid = left + right - left / 2]
    CalcMid --> GetMid[midEmployee = list.get mid]
    GetMid --> CompareTarget[Compare target with midEmployee.id]

    CompareTarget -->|Equal| Found[Found Employee!]
    Found --> DisplayComp1[Display: Completed in X comparisons<br/>Efficiency: Would take up to N with linear]
    DisplayComp1 --> DisplayResult[Display Employee Details]
    DisplayResult --> ReturnEmployee[Return employee]
    ReturnEmployee --> End([End Search])

    CompareTarget -->|Target < Mid| SearchLeft[Search Left Half<br/>right = mid - 1]
    SearchLeft --> CheckBounds

    CompareTarget -->|Target > Mid| SearchRight[Search Right Half<br/>left = mid + 1]
    SearchRight --> CheckBounds

    CheckBounds -->|No| NotFound[Employee Not Found]
    NotFound --> DisplayComp2[Display: Completed in X comparisons<br/>Not found]
    DisplayComp2 --> ReturnNull[Return null]
    ReturnNull --> End

